## ğŸ”¹ Project Overview

This project is a **Java application** that fetches **daily exchange rates** from the **Central Bank of the Republic of Turkey (TCMB)**, lists them to the user, stores the selected currency in a **MySQL database**, and generates a **report comparing todayâ€™s and yesterdayâ€™s rates**.  

It was developed as a **learning-focused project** during my internship to practice **data fetching, processing, and reporting**.

